          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1691681127393-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the meatballs are browned, add the <strong>remaining chopped garlic </strong>to the pan and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong> and <strong>beef stock mix</strong> with 100ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[175ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat, then reduce the heat to medium and cook, covered, for 10-12 min or until cooked through (no pink meat!) – these are your <strong>meatballs & tomato sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1691681144955-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1691681144955-x400.jpg",
